(45, 79, 'Ancient screw barrel for injection jade artifacts dating back 8,500 years, on display in Beijing', '<p>Ancient screw barrel for injection jade artifacts dating back 8,500 years, on display in Beijing<br /><a href="http://ymscrew.com/Product/Injection-molding-screw-and-barrel.html">screw barrel for injection</a> <a href="http://www.colourspray.com/xby/">equipo de pintura electrostatica</a> <a href="http://www.halfdollar.com.cn/pieview.asp?id=447">Dollar Items</a> <a href="http://www.butdress.com/schlichte-brautkleider.html">hof-schleppe brautkleider</a> <a href="http://www.transformerfactory.com/">voltage transformer</a> <a href="http://www.ibc-fittings.com/">quick coupler</a> <a href="http://www.pharma-machines.net/42-hsl_a_capsule_printing_machine.html">capsule printing machines</a> <a href="http://www.easelift.com/">Hand pallet truck</a> <a href="http://www.mantools.net/">Sdconnect compact4</a> <a href="http://www.shenzhenmassageweb.com/">Shenzhen escort</a> <a href="http://www.guangzhoumassagegood.com/">guangzhou escort</a> <a href="http://www.sz-stamping.com/e_index.asp">stamping</a> <a href="http://en.zhong-mu.com/">sanitary butterfly valve</a> <a href="http://www.conplastech.com/en/index.asp?id=77">carrier tape</a> <a href="http://www.cnwzgm.com/">Poker Chip Manufacturer</a> <a href="http://www.diamond-superhard.com/">Industrial diamond</a> <a href="http://www.guanlivalve.com/">knife gate valve</a> <a href="http://www.serve-well.com/docs/eng/oil_property.htm">oil mist collector</a> <a href="http://www.pengfeng.com.tw/pro/list.php?cid=7&amp;f=7">通風工程</a> <a href="http://www.luofuvalve.com/">pressure safety valve</a> <br />Ancient jade artifacts dating back 8,500 years, on display in BeijingPublished: 18 Aug 2009 06:02:01 PST</p>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"> </p>\r\n<p>Ancient jade Dragon. Photo: Xinhua</p>\r\n<p>A collection of 1,368 jade artifacts dating back 8,500 years is now on display in Beijing.</p>\r\n<p>The collection includes a dark green jade dragon in a C shape which is the earliest and best preserved figure of a dragon in Chinese history, according to Professor Lin Yun-teng, from the Department of Geosciences at National Taiwan University, the organizer of the exhibition.</p>\r\n<p>The dragon dates from 5,000 to 6,700 years ago and is a symbol of the Hongshan culture, a neolithic culture that was based in today’s Inner Mongolia and Liaoning and Hebei Provinces, known for their jade jewelry and other items.</p>\r\n<p>Also on show display is jewelry and small sculptures in the shapes of an eagle, insects, flowers, people and mythical sacred animals, dating back 4,000 to 8,500 years ago. Most of the items were used as pendants.</p>\r\n<p>The artifacts were provided by 106 collectors in Taiwan, Hong Kong, Macao and abroad. Most of the articles were unearthed and taken overseas in the early 20th Century, Lin said.</p>\r\n<p>“I hope more mainland visitors can enjoy this wonderful collection and have a better understanding of our traditions with jade,” he added. <br />“This is also part of the effort to improve exchanges across the Taiwan Strait.”</p>\r\n<p>The exhibition at the Chinese Art Museum on Jinyuchi Zhongjie, north of the Temple of Heaven in Beijing, will run until September 18.</p>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n<p align="center">Explore the World, Understand China!<br />Please log on www.gloaltimes.cn</p>\r\n<p><a href="http://www.d0513.com/">搅拌机</a> <a href="http://www.xitongxiazai.com/">XP系统下载</a> <a href="http://www.chinabaoke.net/">减速机</a> <a href="http://www.easthillfx.co.jp/fx/cnc/index5b.htm">外汇保证金交易</a> <a href="http://www.d0513.com/">乳化机</a> <a href="http://www.deao-elevator.com/html/en/en-gsjj.html">elevator manufacturer</a> <a href="http://www.mantools.net/">autoboss V30</a> <a href="http://www.ssfbj.com/fuwu.htm">深圳福田搬家公司</a> <a href="http://www.bestonlinecabinets.com/">ready to assemble kitchen cabinets</a></p>', NULL, '2012-03-24 06:59:34', '2012-03-24 06:59:34', NULL, 10, 0, '00